{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Government measured on delivery of manifesto and commitments to Parliament",
        "additional_details": "Too many promises and election pledges before or during campaigns are not measured in metrics to measure delivery and this system will display it in a easy way for all to see if they have delivered on what they have promised. I want a report for all to see for themselves what has been delivered and what hasn\u2019t and why. It needs to be each year to track progression and for visibility.",
        "background": "1) Publish document on each pledge and promise.\r\n2) Each to be measured by timeline and delivery in a traffic light system.\r\n3) Variance analysis on each line if delivered/pending/not delivered against these metrics in appraisal style measurement.\r\n4) Report available to the public each year.",
